
👽 test linux/amd64

[EXPERIMENTAL]

Display detailed information about a tool from the registry.

USAGE


    $ atmos toolchain info <tool> [flags]


EXAMPLES


    - Display tool info based on the aqua registry


     $ atmos toolchain info <tool>


FLAGS

  -h, --help           help for info

  -o, --output string  Output format (table, yaml, json) (default table)



Use --help=usage for examples or --help=all for all flags and full help.
